      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything just feels so pointless lately. like, i was looking at the stars tonight and it just hit me how much of a joke it all is. we spend our whole lives struggling, working, hurting, just to have it all erased by entropy anyway. in a billion years, none of this even happened. why even bother trying to keep going?",
